            "description": "Return nested Corpus Topic Tree. directFiles/directFaqs contain {id,name,metadata,lecturerOnly,updatedAt}. Optional enrollmentYear and academicYear use metadata range overlap; lecturerOnly=true/false filters exact visibility and omitted means all. Filtered empty branches are hidden and counts/ids are recomputed."
